message: I’m a newbie too. We set up another channel which I’ll link here and it’s full of education resources. If you watch, read or listen to anything you find useful, feel free to add it in there. It’s an open chat ❤️
JS I’m so glad you’re here. And I’m super glad the msging started working. Thank you for the intro. I feel you on the disassociation. That’s been my survival mechanism for a long time
I’m so fucking angry at our representatives and senators and I feel like it’s all a big sham and nothing is ever going to change. I just want to scream and scream and scream.

So about this whole Palestine situation, I feel completely alone and isolated. Even tho I can text my sister and she lives close so we get together once every couple weeks the kids are usually around so we can’t have deep dive conversations and we’re both newbies to this whole thing.

Absolutely I relate to that. I left the work force in May (after literally giving my life to corporate America for 27 years). I thought I’d have so much free time to do all the household chores and projects, BUT NO. My main goal each day is to clean the kitchen ONCE and run the dishwasher before bed. Anything else is a miraculous bonus.

A little about me. I’m 50yo mom w/ 2 teenagers (18, 15) & a husband (who’s in the dog house bc he won’t entertain any convos with me about this). I’m late diagnosed Autistic and I tend to take things very literally and have a hard time FEELING my feelings in my body. I intellectualize or obsessively THINK about things and tend to spend a lot of time dissociating to survive. I’m rbf_meh_smiles on TT. Feel free to ask me anything.

Hi! I just got here & haven’t read previous msgs yet. I’m so excited to have a support group to connect with! The only person IRL I can talk to about any of this is my sister and we’re both like IDK WTF 😫😫😫

My house is a disaster too. We just moved into a new apartment and I don’t have the mental capacity to clean or anything. All I want to do is be on social media to see updates. I am scared to look away because they need our eyes on this. I keep hoping to see that a permanent ceasefire happened.
I feel you 💯

I tend to clean and organize stuff when I feel powerless over a situation, however I am having a very hard time getting work done for my job (I work from home). It feels so meaningless and it's also incredibly hard to stay focused
Hey, I’m not sure if anyone else is feeling this way but I’ve barely had the energy to clean. My space has been so messy and I keep staring at things knowing I should clean it but can’t be bothered.

Hey everyone! We love the informational posts that are being given to us but this group is for us to discuss our personal feeling and lift each other up. So we created an informal group where you can add all the posts you want to share with us! We are going to keep this discussion group as an outlet for discussing personal feelings though. 
Thanks! 😊 
Jelene and Becca.
